 These capabilities will be developed as a series of ECPs for the P-8A and are as follows:
 - ECP 6 - ASW SIGINT, Anti-Submarine Warfare (ASW) capability, Wide Band SATCOM, Higher Than Secret (HTS) processing, Enhanced track management
 (Minotaur), Applications Based Architecture (ABA) and Combat System.
