 Lead Capability Integrator (LCI) integration and award of the Platform Integration (PI) contract to Boeing. ECP 7 integration activities began in FY 2021. ECP 6/7
 Integrated Flight Test & Evaluation began 3Q FY 2022. Enhanced MAC-E (ECP 7) is developed within Program Element (PE) 0604261N and integrated via the Platform
 Integration contract within this PE.

