For imagery processing capabilities, the Air Force uses an incremental acquisition approach with development cycles and spirals to develop, field, and upgrade the
system. Contracts are structured for full and open competition to the maximum extent possible. Additionally, strategic partnerships and agreements with National
Laboratories and other agencies are utilized.




