D. Acquisition Strategy
Program Acquisition Strategy Panel (ASP) approved program's acquisition strategy on 4 Apr 2020. This strategy approved executing an Other Transaction Authority
(OTA) contract to procure proof of concept hardware for test/analysis, award a Sole Source Engineering and Manufacturing Development (EMD) contract to Lockheed
Martin Aerospace for system software and hardware tech insertion, system integration, data management, systems engineering, logistics, test and training to modify 2
aircraft. At completion of EMD, the program would move into Milestone C for Low Rate Initial Production (LRIP) and production to follow.

 Delta ASP approved 12 May 2022 to align EMD contractor requirements and update software development strategy.

 Delta ASP approved 29 Sep 2023 to restructure EMD contractor requirements and include increased scope.




