D. Acquisition Strategy
PTS-G Acquisition strategy was approved by the SAE on 14 August, 2024. The Program Office is working towards a competitive award for an IDIQ contract vehicle and
concurrently a first delivery order for up to four contractors for the design and development of PTS-G vehicles (driving competition between vendors along the vehicle
type (X-Band and mil-Ka Band) or within a single vehicle type). This would be followed by the EMD award, second delivery order, for four vehicles to achieve IOC in FY
2028. A subsequent third delivery order for four more vehicles would achieve FOC in FY 2030. Contract Type is Firm Fixed Price for all PTS-G delivery orders. The 45th
Test Squadron is the PTES Developmental Test Organization and the 4th Test & Evaluation Squadron is the Operational Test organization.




