FY 2025 to FY 2026 Increase/Decrease Statement:
Increase for Research, Development, Test & Evaluation (RDT&E) supports integration and utilization of Machine Learning as the
primary technique to conduct signal processing within the Bounty Hunter (BH) system and ultimately the BH fleet. This technique
is anticipated to reduce manning requirements and accelerate the response time in mission execution taskings for the forward and
remotely deployed BH systems
